es-full-responsibility-ahead-of-fraud-sentencing-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econvicted%20in%20March%20of%20defrauding%20%3C%2Fa%3EJPMorgan%20Chase%2C%20wants%20to%20delay%20her%20September%2029%20sentencing%2C%20saying%20she%20cannot%20fly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20delay%20request%20is%20not%20sitting%20well%20with%20federal%20prosecutors%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-defense-team-gets-warning-after-bothering-jurors-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJavice's%20Manhattan%20judge%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20Monday%2C%20they%20joined%20in%20demanding%20details%20and%20supporting%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20wondered%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20judge%20if%20she%20can%20travel%20by%20train%20or%20car.%20And%20the%20judge%20himself%20asked%20why%2C%20exactly%2C%20can't%20she%20fly%2C%20denying%20the%20delay%2C%20at%20least%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20unable%20to%20grant%20this%20request%2C%20unless%20I%20am%20presented%20with%20evidence%20that%20travel%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20injurious%20to%20Defendant's%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20District%20Court%20Alvin%20K.%20Hellerstein%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20reserved%20all%20day%2C%20September%2029%2C%202025%2C%20for%20sentencing%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Hellerstein%2C%20who%20presided%20over%20Javice's%20trial%20and%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-verdict-frank-startup-guilty-jpmorgan-fraud-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMarch%20conviction%20for%20tricking%20JPMorgan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20largest%20US%20bank%2C%20into%20paying%20%24175%20million%20for%20Frank%2C%20her%20student%20financial%20aid%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20delay%20will%20interfere%20with%20other%20cases%2C%20the%20judge%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20second%20sentencing%20delay%20requested%20by%20Javice%2C%2033%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20the%20Miami%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJavice%20was%20originally%20due%20to%20be%20sentenced%20in%20late%20August.%20That%20date%20was%20pushed%20to%20September%2029%20after%20Javice%20asked%20for%20another%20month%20to%20prepare%20her%20sentencing%20submissions%20and%20deal%20with%20a%20private%20matter%2C%20the%20description%20of%20which%20was%20redacted%20from%20public%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20prosecutors%20did%20not%20oppose%20that%20first%20delay%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they%20are%20opposing%20this%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20letter%20to%20the%20judge%2C%20federal%20prosecutors%20complained%20Monday%20that%20they%20remain%20in%20the%20dark%20over%20%26quot%3Bthe%20specific%20condition%20obviating%20travel%20to%20New%20York.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDefense%20lawyers%20have%20rebuffed%20their%20requests%20for%20more%20detail%20and%20have%20not%20described%20%26quot%3Bthe%20expected%20length%20of%20time%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20travel%20difficulty%20may%20last%2C%20prosecutors%20told%20the%20judge%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJavice's%20delay%20request%20is%20dated%20Thursday%20and%20was%20made%20public%20Monday%2C%20with%20heavy%20redactions%20and%20the%20addition%20of%20the%20judge's%20denial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20notes%20that%20Javice's%20probation%20officer%20does%20not%20oppose%20the%20delay%2C%20and%20was%20signed%20by%20defense%20lawyer%20Ronald%20S.%20Sullivan.%20He%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20prosecutors%20have%20recommended%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprosecutors-recommend-charlie-javice-12-years-prison-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJavice%2C%2033%2C%20serve%2012%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20lying%20to%20JPMorgan%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20her%20website's%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20jury%20found%20Javice%20and%20co-defendant%20Olivier%20Amar%20gave%20the%20bank%20bogus%20spreadsheets%20claiming%20the%20Frank%20website%20had%20amassed%20names%20and%20con