width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Facebook%20Dating%20is%20launching%20an%20AI%20assistant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d18514183847aa39d739e0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFacebook%20Dating%20is%20launching%20an%20AI%20assistant.%3Cp%3EMeta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20is%20launching%20an%20AI%20assistant%20to%20help%20you%20date.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFacebook%20Dating%2C%20the%20company's%20dating%20app%20experience%2C%20rolled%20out%20a%20new%20AI%20feature%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20spoke%20with%20a%20product%20manager%20about%20why%20Facebook%20thinks%20it%20could%20fight%20%26quot%3Bswipe%20fatigue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFacebook%20has%20an%20answer%20for%20swipe%20fatigue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20it's%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-is-beefing-up-its-dating-app-with-new-features-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFacebook%20Dating%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Meta's%20dating%20app%20feature%20housed%20within%20the%20Facebook%20app%2C%20rolled%20out%20an%20AI%20assistant%20on%20Monday%20to%20help%20people%20find%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20really%20tired%20of%20swiping%20through%20hundreds%20of%20profiles%20to%20eventually%20get%20to%20a%20match%20and%20a%20date%2C%26quot%3B%20Neha%20Kumar%2C%20a%20product%20manager%20on%20Facebook%20Dating%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%3A%20How%20can%20we%20tackle%20this%20challenge%20that%20is%20pretty%20pervasive%20in%20dating%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFacebook's%20new%20AI%20dating%20assistant%20is%20a%20chatbot%20experience%20that%20lets%20users%20search%20for%20compatible%20matches%20%E2%80%94%20skipping%20over%20the%20swipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20say%2C%20'find%20someone%20that%20I%20could%20bring%20home%20to%20my%20parents'%20or%20'find%20a%20Brooklyn%20tech%20bro%20who%20would%20go%20to%20EDM%20concerts%20with%20me'%20and%20it'll%20sift%20through%20all%20of%20the%20people%20in%20our%20ecosystem%20and%20find%20the%20right%20person%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Kumar%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20assistant%2C%20built%20using%20Meta's%20Llama%20models%2C%20can%20also%20be%20prompted%20for%20dating%20advice%2C%20such%20as%20troubleshooting%20what%20to%20say%20to%20a%20match%20or%20finding%20a%20first%20date%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnything%20the%20assistant%20recommends%20is%20based%20on%20what's%20publicly%20available%20on%20a%20user's%20profile.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20you%20prompted%20the%20assistant%20to%20find%20someone%20to%20go%20to%20EDM%20concerts%20with%2C%20the%20assistant%20would%20find%20people%20with%20those%20interests%20on%20their%20profiles.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20pulling%20implied%20info%2C%26quot%3B%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20assistant%20is%20not%20one%20of%20Meta's%20AI%20companions%20that%20have%20established%20characters%20that%20resemble%20people%2C%20Kumar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFacebook%20is%20rolling%20out%20its%20AI%20assistant%20feature%20to%20users%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Canada.%20The%20app%20is%20also%20launching%20another%20feature%20called%20%26quot%3BMeet%20Cute%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20automatically%20matches%20users%20with%20another%20person%20based%20on%20Facebook's%20matching%20algorithm%20once%20a%20week.%20(If%20it's%20not%20a%20fit%2C%20you%20can%20unmatch.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2273f5e144-b2d2-4c63-97e5-e3fd300c4475%5C%22%3EFacebook%20Dating%20wants%20young%20adults%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202019%2C%20Facebook%20Dating%20may%20not%20be%20the%20first%20dating%20app%20that%20comes%20to%20mind%2C%20but%20it's%20trying%20to%20pitch%20itself%20to%20young%20users%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20dating%20apps%20like%20Hinge%20or%20Bumble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20has%20no%20monetization%20like%20paywalls%2C%20Kumar%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20very%20much%20don't%20want%20to%20go%20down%20that%20route%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFacebook%20said%20that%20matches%20among%20young%20adults%20are%20up%2010%25%20year%20over%20year%2C%20and%20that%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20young%20adults%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Canada%20make%20FB%20dating%20accounts%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20encourage%20more%20young%20adults%20to%20use%20the%20dating%20feature%2C%20Facebook%20has%20marketing%20campaigns%20lined%20up%2C%20said%20Tiffany%20Lin%2C%20a%20product%20marketing%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Facebook%20will%20run%20a%20%26quot%3Btaildating%26quot%3B%20experience%20at%20the%20State%20Fair%20of%20Texas%2C%20where%20rival%20football%20teams%20for%20the%20University%20of%20Texas%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Oklahoma%20will%20face%20off%2C%20Lin%20said.%20There%2C%20the%20company%20will%20advertise%20FB%20dating's%20recent%20features%2C%20like%20its%20AI%20assistant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e305295b-6579-45ff-b29b-473e6b2dee1a%5C%22%3EAI's%20online%20dating%20takeover%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFacebook's%20not%20the%20first%20to%20pitch%20an%20AI%20solution%20for%20online%20dating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20largest%20dating%20apps%20are%20also%20discussing%20how%20to%20incorporate%20AI%20into%20their%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBumble's%20CEO%20Whitney%20Wolfe%20Herd%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20told%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20last%20month%20that%20the%20company%20is%20developing%20a%20new%20AI-powered%20dating%20experience.%20And%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhinge-ceo-says-ai-could-make-mass-swiping-arcane-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHinge%20CEO%20Justin%20McLeod%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0has%20said%20that%20AI%20could%20improve%20people's%20dating%20app%20experiences%2C%20such%20as%20improving%20matchmaking%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20artic